summary: This is a remake of Aspen Hills, Which is a remake of Lunds Hut,
descriptionHtml:
This mod brings life to this player home it is decorated with things found durning the Journey as Dovahkiin...Has room for two followers to stay...Its in a great location Just outside of Rorikstead..It has a Forge and Armor workbench and a sharpening wheel...There are also Smithing supplies in a Barrel near the Forge...This is a great little place to stop while out on the Road killing dragons, To grab a nap and get some grub...Also a good place for your Companions to hangout when they are not needed...I will be updating this mod frenquently.....If you have ideas or helpful Comments please let me know...

You will need the Latest Version of Skyrim and the Update...

No known conflicks other then mods that change Lunds Hut...

Just Download, Open, Drop file in Data file of Skyrim Folder and Play!
author: Icespiders
